IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
PROGRAM-ID. SIMPLE.

DATA DIVISION.
WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
01 WS-NAME        PIC X(20) VALUE "WORLD".
01 WS-GREETING    PIC X(50).

PROCEDURE DIVISION.
MAIN-PROGRAM.
    STRING "HELLO, " WS-NAME DELIMITED BY SIZE
        INTO WS-GREETING.
    DISPLAY WS-GREETING.
    STOP RUN.
